  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t当年喋血杀二胞<br/>\r\n举国太监媚一个<br/>\r\n突然主子嫌奴少<br/>\r\n遍地交欢叫床高：<br/>\n<br/>\r\n中华奴才真是空前绝后的好动物，生殖器官做爱高潮交欢姿态动作形式幅度大小统统随时随地听从主子招呼教导，只需土匪皇帝领主上头一声令下，交配生殖做爱交欢整齐韵律上下左右听话摇摆千般一律好不壮观生啥操谁都由党来指挥，热闹非凡 —— <br/>\n<b>夜夜床板断三条，</b><br/>\n<b>避孕从此音讯渺，</b><br/>\n<b>一夜回到森林中，</b><br/>\n<b>为党为国操操操</b>！<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS8wMHg0TTFpLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/00x4M1i.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/00x4M1i.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/00x4M1i.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n忆当年 一胎疯：<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9HbHQ5bmNMLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/Glt9ncL.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Glt9ncL.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Glt9ncL.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/38242\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/38242\"><b>乱世笑林</b></a> </div>",
